{
  "stem": "747.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And surely, we very ready to go to the end of the world with them, as long as they-- they giving us food.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we helping them to push that wagon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We went half the night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we're sleeping in the open field that night, and the following day we're walking more.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Around in the early afternoon, we couldn't make it any longer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It just-- my leg wouldn't carry me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- it was an edge of a forest, it was still no-- no leaves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a bare forest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were sitting down, and nursing our sore feet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All of the sudden, a big sound-- a noise coming from the highway.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we looked out, and we saw the first American flag, and the first tank arrived with American soldiers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And within a minute they-- the forest came alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "People whom we didn't know they were hiding there, came and they were kissing their shoes, the boots of these American soldiers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They get frightened for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We looked like from another world-- we're ghosts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they told us that they will send the Red Cross ambulance the following day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was too early for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so we find place in, also another village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the-- the Germans who lived in the town-- the house, they wouldn't let us in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The village, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was the outskirt of Schwerin, on the road to Schwerin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the road to Schwerin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was about a half a day walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, OK, you can go up into the haystack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were-- we settled down there, hungry-- but, eh, you didn't even feel hunger anymore-- and fall asleep.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
